-- American Apparel names Tom Casey as acting president
-- 
-- Fri Oct 8, 2010 8:51am EDT
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2010/10/08/us-americanapparel-president-idUSTRE6972M620101008

 

 NEW YORK  (Reuters) - American Apparel Inc ( APP.A ) said on Friday it has named Tom Casey as acting president. Casey served as CFO of Blockbuster Inc from September 2007 through August 2010. 

